    "documents": "Copy of Eligibility Certificate under West Bengal Textile Incentive Scheme, 2022 as modified from time to time certifying the date of commencement of production. Copy of Udyam Reg./lEM(B). Copy of documents regarding supply of electricity to the unit. Copies of all relevant electricity bills (to be submitted as and when received). Any other documents, if necessary.",
