    "documents": "Aadhaar Copy of SSC/10th certificate & mark sheet, Copy of HSC/12th certificate (In case of Degree level) & mark sheet. Copy of ITI certificate (In case of Lateral Entry for Diploma level) & mark sheet. Copy of Diploma certificate (In case of Lateral Entry for Degree level) & mark sheet. Category Certificate, if applicable. Study/ Bonafide Certificate (Appendix-I). Annual Family Income Certificate (Appendix-II). Promotion Certificate in case of renewal (Appendix-III).",
